Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:04.01,English,,0,0,0,,Finding scorpions in the desert at night is surprisingly easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:04.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,夜间在沙漠中寻找蝎子出乎意料地容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.66,English,,0,0,0,,All you need is an ultraviolet torch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你只需要一个紫外线手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.20,English,,0,0,0,,because scorpions are incredibly fluorescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为蝎子具有令人难以置信的荧光性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:13.21,English,,0,0,0,,Fluorescence means their bodies absorb ultraviolet light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:13.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,荧光意味着它们的身体吸收紫外线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:16.00,English,,0,0,0,,and reradiate it in the visible part of the spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:16.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并将其重新辐射到光谱的可见部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:19.20,English,,0,0,0,,They glow this bright neon green color.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:19.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,蝎子散发这种明亮的霓虹绿色光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:22.34,English,,0,0,0,,But scorpions aren't the only animals that fluoresce.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:22.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但蝎子不是唯一一种散发荧光的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:27.65,English,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish, amphibians, owls, and even platypus glow under ultraviolet light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:27.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,水母、两栖动物、猫头鹰甚至是鸭嘴兽都会在紫外线下发光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.70,English,,0,0,0,,I'm out here in the desert near Bakersfield, California,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在在加州贝克斯菲尔德附近的沙漠中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.93,English,,0,0,0,,looking for scorpions with Carl Kloock,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和 Carl Kloock 一起找寻蝎子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:37.30,English,,0,0,0,,a professor of biology at Cal State Bakersfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:37.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他是加州州立大学贝克斯菲尔德分校的生物学教授
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.97,English,,0,0,0,,He's been researching scorpion fluorescence for over a decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他研究蝎子的荧光性已经超过十年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.90,English,,0,0,0,,- If you have a black light it's really pretty easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 如果你有黑光灯的话，寻找蝎子真的十分容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(3080,1910)}“黑光灯”即长波紫外线灯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.23,English,,0,0,0,,If they're there, you're going to spot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果蝎子在那，你就能看见它们\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:48.39,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Does he look like he's in a posture to like defend himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:48.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 它看起来像不像处于防卫姿势？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:49.42,English,,0,0,0,,- [Carl] Yeah, he's not real happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:49.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 是的，它不太高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:50.20,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:50.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.00,English,,0,0,0,,- [Carl] I'm going to grab my high-tech scorpion catching equipment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 在此我要拿出我的高科技捕蝎装置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.97,English,,0,0,0,,It's a tongue depressor with a yellow highlighter on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是个压舌板，上面涂了黄色荧光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.67,English,,0,0,0,,So it fluoresces in black light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它在黑光灯下会散发荧光，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:00:59.85,English,,0,0,0,,So you can see where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:00:59.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因此你能看见它在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:00.33,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:00.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:04.46,English,,0,0,0,,- [Carl] This technique is usually to put the vial behind him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:04.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 抓蝎子的技巧是将瓶子放在蝎子身后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:07.80,English,,0,0,0,,then in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:07.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,压舌板放在蝎子身前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:10.29,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] That was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:10.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 蛮牛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:12.29,English,,0,0,0,,\NAll right. Should we give it a shot?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:12.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的。我们也试一试？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.11,English,,0,0,0,,Got one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,找到了一只
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:20.11,English,,0,0,0,,- [Carl] Just gently pokes him back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:20.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 轻轻地将它戳进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:22.87,English,,0,0,0,,And they usually just kind of do a little side crab walk back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:22.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们往往会像螃蟹一样横着走\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.07,English,,0,0,0,,There you go, and just tilt it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就这样，把它倾斜起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:27.95,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:27.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:30.01,English,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:30.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,难以置信！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:32.01,English,,0,0,0,,All right. I'm going to get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:32.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，我一定要抓到他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:34.93,English,,0,0,0,,But why are scorpions fluorescent?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:34.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是为什么蝎子有荧光性？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:36.55,English,,0,0,0,,- I've got about 12 hypotheses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:36.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我有大约 12 种假说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.98,English,,0,0,0,,So you test them one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一次测试它们中的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:41.07,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] You've got 12 Hypotheses about why the scorpions fluoresce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:41.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 你有关于蝎子为什么散发荧光的12 种假说？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.74,English,,0,0,0,,- More like six actually, I was being a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,实际上更像是 6 个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.88,English,,0,0,0,,Almost all scorpions fluoresce.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几乎所有的蝎子都有荧光性\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:47.18,English,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen it myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:47.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我自己没有亲眼见过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:50.56,English,,0,0,0,,but some that live in caves that don't fluoresce
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:50.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是有些居住在洞穴中的蝎子不散发荧光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.35,English,,0,0,0,,but it's only like one very small group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过它们在蝎子的族群中少之又少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.68,English,,0,0,0,,All the other scorpions fluoresce.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,其他所有的蝎子都散发荧光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:57.36,English,,0,0,0,,One possibility is just, this is a Relic Trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:57.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有一种可能，这是一种遗留特征\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:02.22,English,,0,0,0,,It's something they developed way back when they first came out on land and just haven't lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:02.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是自他们从这片陆地上诞生就有的特征，一直保留到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:06.13,English,,0,0,0,,A chemical that has another function that just happens to fluoresce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:06.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一种有着其他功能的化学物质正巧会散发荧光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:08.13,English,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of chemicals that fluoresce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:08.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有许多化学物质都会散发荧光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.50,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, we have internal bodily fluids that fluoresce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，我们体内有会散发荧光的体液
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.50,English,,0,0,0,,And clearly those are never exposed to UV light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而显然，这些从来没有暴露在紫外线下\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.78,English,,0,0,0,,So the idea of having a function for that fluorescence is kind of silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以专门有一个荧光功能的这种想法有些愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.81,English,,0,0,0,,This fluoresce is about the same color as a scorpion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个荧光颜色和蝎子的荧光颜色一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.29,English,,0,0,0,,but clearly isn't a scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但这显然不是个蝎子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.38,English,,0,0,0,,It's actually a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它实际上是一块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.69,English,,0,0,0,,The color is a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,颜色有点偏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.88,English,,0,0,0,,\N- [Derek] But that is like, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 但那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:27.94,English,,0,0,0,,- It's plastic from a water bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:27.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它是块塑料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:29.02,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:29.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 呵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:34.18,English,,0,0,0,,You wanted to know if the scorpions were fluorescing in order to attract insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:34.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你想知道蝎子发出荧光是不是为了吸引昆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:34.51,English,,0,0,0,,- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:34.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.86,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] So how did you test that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 你是怎么测试这个假说的？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.56,English,,0,0,0,,- What I did was I used preserved scorpions like these ones
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我使用了抓到的蝎子，例如这些\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:43.18,English,,0,0,0,,and I took half of them and dip them in UV blocking marine varnish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:43.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我将蝎子等分成两组，将一组浸入阻隔紫外线的船舶清漆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.50,English,,0,0,0,,so they didn't fluoresce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样一来他们不会散发荧光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.25,English,,0,0,0,,\NAnd then I just used basically flypaper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,之后我就使用捕蝇纸之类的东西，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.92,English,,0,0,0,,and took those things outside and set them side by side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,将他们放在户外并排摆放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:53.00,English,,0,0,0,,and then found the number of flying insects
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:53.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,观察各个捕蝇纸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.89,English,,0,0,0,,that were caught in each.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,捕捉到的飞虫数量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:55.16,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:55.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:56.59,English,,0,0,0,,- [Carl] So we were outside in moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:56.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们在野外的月光下\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:00.95,English,,0,0,0,,and I did the same experiment, both under the new moon and the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:00.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,同样的实验在新月时和满月时都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.91,English,,0,0,0,,And so what I found from that was when there was a new moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我从实验中发现新月之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.95,English,,0,0,0,,there was no difference in the number of insects caught by the fluorescent and non-fluorescent scorpions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,散发荧光的蝎子与不散发荧光的蝎子捕捉到的昆虫数量没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.03,English,,0,0,0,,\NBut under the full moon, there's nice, bright UV light available there was a difference
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是在满月下，有充足、明亮的紫外光时，捕捉到的昆虫数量有差别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.68,English,,0,0,0,,and the ones that fluoresce actually caught fewer insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,散发荧光的蝎子所吸引的昆虫反而更少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.54,English,,0,0,0,,- It seems kind of counterintuitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这似乎有点违反直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.01,English,,0,0,0,,- So that tells me that my hypothesis was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这意味着我的假说是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.18,English,,0,0,0,,Which happens a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这常常发生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.68,English,,0,0,0,,\NBasically yeah, they're not using their fluorescence to lure insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大体上说，蝎子并不使用荧光来引诱昆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:28.94,English,,0,0,0,,In fact, the fluorescence is a bad thing for them in terms of their ability to catch flying insects, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:28.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,实际上，就其捕捉飞虫的能力而言荧光对它们来说是一件坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.43,English,,0,0,0,,- Let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我问你一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.44,English,,0,0,0,,If you find that fluorescence is counterproductive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你发现荧光在某些方面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.19,English,,0,0,0,,for the scorpion in some way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对蝎子没有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.15,English,,0,0,0,,doesn't that indicate that there has to be something useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这难道不意味着在某些方面是有用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.20,English,,0,0,0,,- Exactly. There must be something that counteracts that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 确实。一定有什么可以抵消荧光带来的坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.93,English,,0,0,0,,- Sort of negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 不全是坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.04,English,,0,0,0,,- That negative, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 是的，某些方面有害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:45.55,English,,0,0,0,,Scorpions are really well adapted for what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:45.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,蝎子因为习性做出很大改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.92,English,,0,0,0,,One of the cool things here is it scorpions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比较酷的一点是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:52.70,English,,0,0,0,,are actually able to metabolize iron and nickel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:52.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,蝎子实际上能够代谢铁和镍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.76,English,,0,0,0,,And in their pincer here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们的毒刺这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.20,English,,0,0,0,,and on the tips of their claws,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及它们的钳肢前端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:01.24,English,,0,0,0,,they actually have basically iron to strengthen that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:01.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们用铁来强化这些部位\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.58,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Iron and nickel at the end of their tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 在它们的尾部末端有铁和镍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:05.80,English,,0,0,0,,- [Carl] Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:05.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 是的，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:09.20,English,,0,0,0,,You can see like the color here's a little bit different and that's because of the iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:09.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以看出这边的颜色有一点不同这是因为有铁元素
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.97,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] That seems very aggressive to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样感觉好暴掠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.16,English,,0,0,0,,One of the main things we're interested in here is how they see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们主要好奇的一件事情是蝎子是如何看见东西的\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.18,English,,0,0,0,,So I've seen two of their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我看见了他的两只眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:21.13,English,,0,0,0,,- [Carl] So, those are the median eyes right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:21.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这是它的中眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.28,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Those two dark spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这两个小黑点\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.25,English,,0,0,0,,- [Carl] Yeah. There's a cluster of three eyes right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 没错。这边有 3 个侧眼扎堆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.44,English,,0,0,0,,And of course on the other side, so they're symmetrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,另外一边也有，这对称的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.07,English,,0,0,0,,So they have a total of eight eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以蝎子一共有 8 只眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:32.29,English,,0,0,0,,- Can they detect the light with parts of their body that are not eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:32.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 他们能用除眼睛之外的身体部位探测光照吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.29,English,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. Actually they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的，它们确实可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.29,English,,0,0,0,,
